      "stem": "A 5-week-old infant is brought in by parents for vomiting. Parents state the vomiting has been increasingly forceful over the last week and most commonly occurs 15 minutes after feeding. Between episodes, the infant continues to appear hungry. There has been no associated fever, diarrhea, or apparent abdominal pain. What is the MOST LIKELY diagnosis?",
